title: torch-0.2.0.post1-cp27-cp27m-manylinux1_x86_64.whl is not a supported wheel on this platform.
body_html:
I am trying to upgrade my pytorch via using pip command from the website.
I have ubuntu 16.04.
Should I remove my pytorch first?
when I run the command on the website I receive this error:
torch-0.2.0.post1-cp27-cp27m-manylinux1_x86_64.whl is not a supported wheel on this platform.

Any suggestion what I need to do?
Also pip --version gives me: pip 9.0.1 from /usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages (python 2.7)

Thanks
